Class Precondition

java.lang.Object
  m0rjc.ax25.generator.model.Precondition
Direct Known Subclasses:
CompositePrecondition, FlagCheckPrecondition, VariableValuePrecondition
public abstract class Precondition
extends Object

A precondition that can be applied to a Transition. Preconditions are immutable, so instances can be reused.
